        @{u}@{b}@{fg highlight}ST:CCG Card of the day@{fg text}@{ub}@{uu}

        @{b}Wesley's STCCG card of the day #149@{ub}

Hi, folks,

here's a Dilemma to use against the rich kids (that's those with
the Future Enterprise that still evades me):


    @{b}RASCALS@{ub}

    Dilemma, Space, uncommon AU.

All unique crew members (maximum of 4, random selection) are kids.
STRENGTH = 2 and Youth replaces first-listed skill. Cure with 2
MEDICAL and Biology.

@{i}"Passing through a molecular reversion field in a shuttle, Guinan,
@{"Ro Laren" link "STCCG:cotd100.guide/COTD92"}, Keiko O'Brien and @{"Jean-Luc Picard" link "STCCG:cotd100.guide/COTD1"} reverted to children's
bodies but retained adult knowledge."@{ui}


Well, this card somewhat missed its goal. It was intended as a fix
against the players with all the great Bridge crew. Now just look
at what happens instead:

Player 1 has a starter and 6 boosters, thus 39 uncommons and rares.
Assuming he plays Fed, he'll probably have around 6 unique personnel
and he's gonna use them all in order to stand a chance. So he'll
have four or less in an average away team and his best guys are all
affected :-(

Player 2 is a rich one with a complete set of everything. In her 18
personnel cards she has 17 uniques (just @{"Vekor" link "STCCG:cotd100.guide/COTD37"} cause she's great).
She'll lose the use of one or two of her top five crew, but not four.

Net result: This card hurts the player with few options more than the
really rich one.

Also, note the great effect of this card on @{"Wes" link "STCCG:cotd100.guide/COTD26"}: Youth gets replaced
by Youth!

Still, Rascals might offer great combo opportunities when used with
Dilemmas that require Strength. El-Adrel creatures, Chalnoths, Rebel
Encounters and Malfunctioning doors would be good choices, but they're
all planets. Just where are the Space Dilemmas with Strength require-
ments?

Best comparison: @{"Tsiolkovsky infection" link COTD128}. Similar effect, though more
personnel affected and no Strength loss. Also, similar cure (though
Rascals seems a bit easier if you can get @{"Bev Crusher" link "STCCG:cotd100.guide/COTD22"} to remain
unaffected). Almost equal game value. Average. Next.


Favorite combo(s):

- Rascals + Interphasic Plasma Creatures: 2 - 2 = !!!!!


