Leadership-Honor-Diplomacy skill combination, but adding a SECURITY and
the Navigation ability to this makes a formidable Klingon with the added
bonus of having two classifications for the @{"Naiskos" link "STCCG:cotd100.guide/COTD13"} (Try Governor Worf +
@{"Vekor" link "STCCG:cotd100.guide/COTD37"} + Bok + Berlingoff Rasmussen in an IKC Fek'Ihr for an
all-but-unstoppable ship of 33/27/24. Now just add a @{"Bynars Weapon enhancements" link COTD197}
