@{i}"Disguised serpentine alien device used by the Devidians. When irradiated
with the correct energy, the head comes alive and allows Devidians to
control their time travel."@{ui}


So this is the first card that cannot be used on its own at all.
Now, its three uses:

1) Triple a @{"Devidian door" link COTD146}. I think I've already detailed the advantages
