Hi, folks,

Magic-ians have their Crusades, we have


    @{b}LOWER DECKS@{ub}

    Event, uncommon AU.

Plays on table. While in play, all of your non-holographic, universal
personnel are each CUNNING +2, INTEGRITY +2 and STRENGTH +2 (Not
cumulative.)

@{i}"Junior officers aboard all starships cooperate in their duties while
competing for promotion and advancement, such as Ensigns Taurik, Sito,
