A good card for our green pointy-eared friends. They have by far the best
universal personnel (and the worst uniques) and work well together with
the non-aligned universals. Klingon and Federation decks have far less to
gain from this card as these afiliations cannot sport good universals and
also have less to gain from some extra attribute points.

The best deck design for this card is a stall deck, a deck type well
suited for Romulans. You can
