  quite sure not to lose anybody to Firestorms.
- combine it with @{"Klim Dokachim" link COTD178} to delay your opponent
- start away team battles with your powered-up crews
- tolerate a pretty slow development of your own forces, instead making
  sure your opponent's development is even worse.

